Create Both
# Expunge Both
# SyncState *

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# maps

IMAPAccount maps
Host imap.one.com
User maps@dahl-jacobsen.dk
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mutt/accounts/maps.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

# Remote storage
IMAPStore maps-remote
Account maps

# Local storage
MaildirStore maps-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/maps/
Inbox ~/mail/maps/Inbox

Channel maps
Master :maps-remote:
Slave :maps-local:
Patterns *
Sync All

Channel maps-inbox
Master :maps-remote:
Slave :maps-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Sync Pull


